   Hannah, 47, wowed on the astroturf-style carpet as she posed up a storm in a dress almost the same colour as the dark green grass. The garment featured a low scoop neckline and an exposed back. The bodycon, which came down to just above Hannah’s ankles, fit tightly to accentuate the actress’ incredible curves. Hannah wore her blonde hair tied back in a simple ponytail and accessorised with some sparkly, drop-down earrings.  